The only issue with modern technology here is that it is susceptible to modern vulnerabilities. Even if we can prevent things like the weapon systems from being hacked and operated remotely, it is still vulnerable to other forms of electronic warfare. In the worst case scenario where all the advanced electronic systems go down, would the crew still be able to operate their vessel and perform their mission? Based on the heavy reliance on tech, I cannot see how they would.
